  <official_title>A Randomized, Comparative Study of the Effects of Candesartan and Telmisartan on the Home Blood Pressure, Glucose and Lipid Metabolism in the Hypertensive Patients With the Accumulation of Visceral Fat by the Central Registration System</official_title>
