  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      To investigate the effects of Candesartan and Telmisartan on the home blood pressure, glucose
      and lipid-metabolism in the hypertensive patients with the accumulation of visceral fat by
      the newly developed Tele-medicine system
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      A randomized, comparative study of the effects of Candesartan and Telmisartan on the home
      blood pressure, glucose and lipid metabolism in the hypertensive patients with the
      accumulation of visceral fat by the central registration system
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
